name: Jaime L. Garcia
text: The reason why I said the definition of veggies are everything that everything else is not is because the definition is arbitrary. Ask vegetarians what they can or cannot eat, and you get different answers (though this is more a meat anti-definition , than plant-part distinction between fruit and veggie or goodness knows what else).
